# RICK-OS · environment variables reference
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# RULE: never commit real secrets. This file is safe to commit because it only
# contains the public anon key (which is safe) and placeholders for secrets.
#
# Where each variable actually lives:
#   Frontend    → Vercel dashboard (or .env.local locally — git-ignored)
#   Python      → integrations/python/.env (git-ignored)
#   Apps Script → Script Properties in script.google.com
#   Edge Fn     → Supabase → Edge Functions → wallet-ingest → Secrets
#   GitHub CI   → GitHub → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions

# ── 1. Frontend (Vite / Vercel) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# New project: oslife (nhyunnnmdcmojvkxrbpl, eu-west-1)
# Get the anon key from: Supabase dashboard → nhyunnnmdcmojvkxrbpl → Settings → API → anon/public
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://nhyunnnmdcmojvkxrbpl.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<anon key from Supabase dashboard → nhyunnnmdcmojvkxrbpl → Settings → API>

# ── 2. Python ingestion scripts (integrations/python/.env) ────────────────────
# Copy this block into integrations/python/.env and fill in the secrets.
# That file is git-ignored — never commit it.
SUPABASE_URL=https://nhyunnnmdcmojvkxrbpl.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=<service_role key — Supabase → nhyunnnmdcmojvkxrbpl → Settings → API>
RICK_USER_ID=1b0f7cc3-cc39-43ae-92fe-9866c1c381a9

# Spotify — only needed for spotify_poll.py and ingest_spotify.py --enrich
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=<from developer.spotify.com → your app>
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=<from developer.spotify.com → your app>
SPOTIFY_REFRESH_TOKEN=<run: python integrations/python/spotify_poll.py --auth>

# ── 3. Apps Script — set in Script Properties (script.google.com) ────────────
# NOT stored here. Add these manually in the Apps Script editor:
#   SUPABASE_URL          https://nhyunnnmdcmojvkxrbpl.supabase.co
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY  <service_role key>
#   RICK_USER_ID          1b0f7cc3-cc39-43ae-92fe-9866c1c381a9
#   NOTION_TOKEN          secret_xxx (from notion.so → Settings → Integrations)
#   NOTION_DB_ID          239ddc8e920881edad44ea304bf4d47d
#   PAYMENTS_CAL_ID       <your Google Calendar ID ending in @group.calendar.google.com>

# ── 4. Supabase Edge Functions — set in Supabase dashboard ───────────────────
# Supabase → Project nhyunnnmdcmojvkxrbpl → Edge Functions → Manage secrets:
#   RICK_USER_ID          1b0f7cc3-cc39-43ae-92fe-9866c1c381a9
